  "help": {
    "title": "Help",
    "pageHelp": "Page Help",
    "dashboard": "This page shows an overview of your contracts, costs, and upcoming deadlines. Click the KPI tiles to navigate directly to the relevant section. Under 'Expiring Contracts' you can see contracts whose cancellation deadline is approaching.",
    "contracts": "Manage your contracts here. Use the filter bar to filter by category or status. Switch between card and list view. Use the '+ Add Contract' button to create new contracts.",
    "contractDetail": "This page shows all details of a contract: costs, duration, renewals, and reminders. You can edit the contract, leave comments, and enable or disable reminders.",
    "analytics": "The cost overview shows your monthly and yearly expenses, broken down by category and provider. In the table view you can filter by date range — all contracts valid during the selected period are shown. Click a contract to open its details.",
    "deadlines": "Here you can see all upcoming cancellation deadlines, sorted by urgency. Overdue deadlines are marked in red. Export deadlines as an .ics file for your calendar.",
    "templates": "Create cancellation letters based on your contract data. Select the contract and template — data is filled in automatically. Download as PDF or DOCX.",
    "notifications": "Here you can find all notifications about your contracts. Mark individual ones as read or mark all as read.",
    "organization": "Manage your company, members, and contract categories. As an admin you can invite members and assign roles.",
    "profile": "Edit your personal information and change your password. You can export or delete your data according to GDPR.",
    "settings": "Adjust language and appearance."
  },
